## Prerequisites

You have to be enthusiastic and have a growth mindset and a desire to learn

## Steps 

Download and install xcode
Buy an udemy course on programmatic ios dev

### Creating a New iOS App

First lauch your xcode dev app and go to new single page view application and proceed from there

